title: Solo Andy Colt Bass
description:
This is the first solo (limited edition cd) from Andy, the bass player in The 

Colt .45s presented to the guests at his private New Year's Eve gig and party.  

The cd covers featured real leaves and no two were the same.


As well as lead and bass guitar, Andy plays the mandolin, dulcimer, bongo drum, 

drum machine and keyboards on this cd.
